##
## This PCD specifies which terminal type is used by the remote console
## when redirecting BIOS screens.
## 1 - VT52. Note: Not supported in BIOS.
## 2 - VT100+. Note: No longer supported in Intel CSME 14.0 and later.
## 3 - VT-UTF8
## 4 - PC-ANSI
## 5 and higher - reserved for future definitions
##
